text: Maly Muynak () is a rural locality (a village) in Surensky Selsoviet, Zianchurinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 96 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 18 km from Isyangulovo, 5 km from Kugarchi. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zianchurinsky District
title: Maly Muynak
